<view class="container fade-in">
  <view class="header-section">
    <view class="icon-wrapper">
      <text class="iconfont icon-coffee" style="font-size: 80rpx; color: #ff6b81;"></text>
    </view>
    <text class="title">感谢您的支持</text>
    <text class="subtitle">您的鼓励是我坚持更新的最大动力</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="message-box">
      <view class="quote-start">“</view>
      <text class="message-text">开发维护不易，如果您觉得这个小工具对您的工作有所帮助，不妨请我喝杯咖啡吧！☕️ \n\n每一份支持都将投入到服务器维护和新功能的开发中。</text>
      <view class="quote-end">”</view>
    </view>

    <view class="qr-section">
      <view class="qr-container">
        <!-- Placeholder for the QR Code -->
        <image class="qr-code" src="{{qrCodeUrl}}" mode="aspectFit" show-menu-by-longpress></image>
        <view class="scan-tip">长按保存图片或识别</view>
      </view>
      <view class="payment-methods">
        <view class="method active">
          <text class="iconfont icon-wechat"></text> 微信支付
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text>© 2026 Made with LeanOn❤️</text>
  </view>
</view>
